[The Price of Pursuing Beauty]</i>

34
00:02:14,690 --> 00:02:17,500
Makeup is necessary. Most foreign girls wear makeup.

35
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:21,030
But besides you, no one else around me wears makeup.

36
00:02:21,030 --> 00:02:23,271
Tang Ya, do you wear makeup?

37
00:02:23,271 --> 00:02:24,973
I...

38
00:02:26,780 --> 00:02:29,170
It's not allowed in school. You're going to host the foreign guests.

39
00:02:29,170 --> 00:02:30,850
Wearing makeup is etiquette.

40
00:02:30,850 --> 00:02:32,780
I should put on some makeup then.

41
00:02:32,780 --> 00:02:34,410
I have to leave a good impression on them for our school. Right?

42
00:02:34,410 --> 00:02:36,340
Do you have cosmetics? I can do the makeup for you.

43
00:02:36,340 --> 00:02:38,201
I do. Dabao SOD lotion.

44
00:02:38,201 --> 00:02:40,511
Come on. That's what my dad uses. Okay?

45
00:02:40,511 --> 00:02:43,050
I'm talking about foundation.

46
00:02:43,050 --> 00:02:44,533
Eye shadow?

47
00:02:44,533 --> 00:02:47,070
Blush and lipstick?

48
00:02:47,070 --> 00:02:48,750
Are you a girl?

49
00:02:48,750 --> 00:02:50,310
Well, my mom doesn't have any either.

50
00:02:50,310 --> 00:02:53,380
- Would you lend me yours?
- No problem.

51
00:02:53,380 --> 00:02:56,030
Come to my home after school, I'll test the makeup on you.

52
00:02:56,030 --> 00:02:57,570
But your mom is at home.

53
00:02:57,570 --> 00:03:01,180
- Let's go to Zhang Qi's home then. Ms. Zhang Ling may not be at home.
- Okay.

54
00:03:01,180 --> 00:03:04,460
Shiyin, I brought you some chocolate.

55
00:03:04,460 --> 00:03:07,010
I'm on a diet.

56
00:03:07,010 --> 00:03:09,280
This must be delicious.

57
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,770
This is a new product. Try it.

58
00:03:11,770 --> 00:03:13,610
I don't eat chocolate.

59
00:03:16,330 --> 00:03:19,210
Xue, have another piece.

60
00:03:21,090 --> 00:03:23,320
Tang Ya, have some too.

61
00:03:36,060 --> 00:03:38,111
You didn't come home after you got off work.

62
00:03:38,111 --> 00:03:40,611
Where did you go? Why didn't you cook?

63
00:03:42,010 --> 00:03:44,080
I went to buy some pears for her.

64
00:03:44,080 --> 00:03:46,530
She'll be interpreting tomorrow and talking the entire day.

65
00:03:46,530 --> 00:03:49,700
I'll brew some pear soup for her to ease her throat.

66
00:03:49,700 --> 00:03:51,030
Look at you.

67
00:03:51,030 --> 00:03:52,980
You keep nagging her every day.

68
00:03:52,980 --> 00:03:56,190
But in your heart, you always think about her.

69
00:04:00,250 --> 00:04:03,520
Well, how would she think you're a great dad

70
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:05,800
if I didn't play the devil?

71
00:04:07,360 --> 00:04:10,200
- Has she come home?
- Come back. Come back.

72
00:04:10,200 --> 00:04:12,250
But she finds you annoying.

73
00:04:12,250 --> 00:04:14,120
She went to study English at Zhang Qi's.

74
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,930
She finds me annoying?

75
00:04:15,930 --> 00:04:17,850
What's the matter with this kid?

76
00:04:17,850 --> 00:04:20,360
Exactly, I'll lecture her.

77
00:04:21,130 --> 00:04:23,990
Okay. Go. This kid...

78
00:04:28,140 --> 00:04:29,470
It's good that you didn't peel the scallion.

79
00:04:29,470 --> 00:04:31,260
Otherwise, you'd make it bald.

80
00:04:31,260 --> 00:04:33,330
I can do this myself.

81
00:04:37,800 --> 00:04:39,600
You only have this one lipstick?

82
00:04:40,820 --> 00:04:43,180
My mom has locked up my cosmetics.

83
00:04:43,180 --> 00:04:44,820
Well, let's use this lipstick only.

84
00:04:44,820 --> 00:04:47,480
No way. You must apply full makeup.

85
00:04:47,480 --> 00:04:49,310
Shall I borrow some from Ms. Jin Ning?

86
00:04:49,310 --> 00:04:50,843
No way.

87
00:04:50,843 --> 00:04:52,920
What if she tells my mom?

88
00:04:52,920 --> 00:04:55,370
- It will be exposed then.
- No way.

89
00:04:56,720 --> 00:04:58,970
I always go to play my role at a critical moment.

90
00:04:58,970 --> 00:05:00,603
Wait for me.

91
00:05:03,020 --> 00:05:05,920
Come on, Xue. Let's try it on you.

92
00:05:10,140 --> 00:05:12,800
Okay. Do your makeup.

93
00:05:12,800 --> 00:05:14,413
What is this?

94
00:05:16,260 --> 00:05:18,820
- So many?
- As expected of Ms. Zhang Ling.

95
00:05:18,820 --> 00:05:20,970
These are premium cosmetics.

96
00:05:20,970 --> 00:05:22,370
Are these expensive?

97
00:05:22,400 --> 00:05:25,200
Let me tell you. Any of these is as expensive as a PS2.

98
00:05:25,271 --> 00:05:27,723
- That expensive?
- Yeah!

99
00:05:27,723 --> 00:05:29,530
I'd have sold them secretly if I had known earlier.

100
00:05:29,530 --> 00:05:31,060
My mom doesn't use them anyway.

101
00:05:31,060 --> 00:05:34,010
Ms. Zhang Ling doesn't wear makeup?

102
00:05:34,010 --> 00:05:36,361
She? She doesn't even wash her face when she's busy.

103
00:05:36,361 --> 00:05:38,410
Where does she find the time to apply makeup?

104
00:05:38,410 --> 00:05:39,950
What a pity.

105
00:05:39,950 --> 00:05:42,940
If anyone gave me these, I'd order the TV show "The Little Li Flying Dagger" dedicated to the person for one year.

106
00:05:42,940 --> 00:05:45,280
Look at you. You already have enough cosmetics.

107
00:05:45,280 --> 00:05:46,970
You still want more?

108
00:05:48,480 --> 00:05:50,213
Come on, Xue.

109
00:06:01,100 --> 00:06:03,250
Please stay away.

110
00:06:03,250 --> 00:06:05,740
This is my home. Where can I go?

111
00:06:05,740 --> 00:06:08,410
You... Buy us some snacks.

112
00:06:08,410 --> 00:06:10,530
I don't feel comfortable with you here.

113
00:06:10,530 --> 00:06:12,590
Eat this on your way. I don't like this.

114
00:06:12,590 --> 00:06:14,050
There are so many snacks here already!

115
00:06:14,050 --> 00:06:16,650
Not enough. Off you go.

116
00:06:18,660 --> 00:06:22,430
We won't see you off. Don't come back before we call you.

117
00:06:25,290 --> 00:06:26,623
Come on.

118
00:06:31,220 --> 00:06:33,960
<i>[Colorful Peanuts]</i>
35 peanuts. 36 peanuts.

119
00:06:33,960 --> 00:06:36,500
37 peanuts. 38 peanuts.

120
00:06:36,500 --> 00:06:39,220
39 peanuts. 40 peanuts.

121
00:06:39,220 --> 00:06:41,590
41 peanuts. 42 peanuts.

122
00:06:41,590 --> 00:06:44,020
43 peanuts. 44 peanuts.

123
00:06:44,020 --> 00:06:46,070
<i>[Haircut. Perm. Hair treatment]</i>

124
00:06:46,070 --> 00:06:49,660
Why are you back so late? I was so bored.

125
00:06:49,660 --> 00:06:53,470
- Why are you sitting here?
- I was kicked out.

126
00:06:53,470 --> 00:06:56,010
Why are you back so late?

127
00:07:00,730 --> 00:07:02,820
Compulsory extra class.

128
00:07:02,820 --> 00:07:05,170
12th Grade is indeed a crazy year.

129
00:07:06,150 --> 00:07:08,950
Isn't it the same for your competition class?

130
00:07:08,950 --> 00:07:10,303
Forget it.

131
00:07:10,303 --> 00:07:12,310
Those in the competition class are even crazier.

132
00:07:12,310 --> 00:07:14,610
They don't go home after school but keep studying there.

133
00:07:14,610 --> 00:07:16,610
I regret transferring to that class.

134
00:07:17,800 --> 00:07:19,670
- I'm leaving.
- Bye.

135
00:07:19,670 --> 00:07:21,960
Sunian, you're home.

136
00:07:24,530 --> 00:07:28,513
How is it? Are you stunned by my excellent makeup skills?

137
00:07:37,470 --> 00:07:39,930
Just ignore them. This is the makeup style for the camera.

138
00:07:39,930 --> 00:07:42,700
It's different from the one for daily life. They can't appreciate it.

139
00:07:43,720 --> 00:07:48,010
Well, I've completed my mission. I'm leaving. Bye.

140
00:07:56,700 --> 00:07:58,333
Do I look good?

141
00:08:01,680 --> 00:08:04,300
Nice. Nice.

142
00:08:09,900 --> 00:08:12,040
Sunian, do I look good?

143
00:08:16,780 --> 00:08:18,580
I can't say it's bad.

144
00:08:18,580 --> 00:08:21,230
Then, why didn't you say anything just now?

145
00:08:24,290 --> 00:08:27,960
I still prefer how you usually look.

146
00:08:30,970 --> 00:08:32,620
Lin Shiyin

147
00:08:32,620 --> 00:08:35,720
gave herself beautiful makeup but mine's ugly.

