180
00:10:24,723 --> 00:10:28,020
♫ <i>Those troubles that we never told each other</i> ♫

181
00:10:29,300 --> 00:10:31,210
I never lie to you.

182
00:10:32,730 --> 00:10:35,360
Let's go.

183
00:11:03,150 --> 00:11:05,650
Xue.

184
00:11:05,650 --> 00:11:08,060
Why are you home so late?

185
00:11:08,820 --> 00:11:12,500
I just simulated tomorrow's visit with Zhang Qi.

186
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:14,800
It took a bit more time.

187
00:11:14,800 --> 00:11:16,140
I've brewed some pear soup for you.

188
00:11:16,140 --> 00:11:19,150
It's on the table. Drink it now.

189
00:11:23,920 --> 00:11:25,130
What are you doing?

190
00:11:25,130 --> 00:11:27,120
I'm dancing.

191
00:11:27,120 --> 00:11:29,420
Mom, you should go to bed now.

192
00:11:31,750 --> 00:11:34,400
Go to bed early after finishing it.

193
00:11:34,400 --> 00:11:35,610
Mom, good night.

194
00:11:35,610 --> 00:11:37,280
Good night.

195
00:12:04,320 --> 00:12:07,750
What did Lin Shiyin do with the makeup?

196
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:13,500
Why do I feel itchy?

197
00:12:15,610 --> 00:12:17,350
So itchy.

198
00:12:27,090 --> 00:12:28,460
- Xue.
- Mr. Liu.

199
00:12:28,460 --> 00:12:29,950
Have a seat.

200
00:12:29,950 --> 00:12:32,450
The delegation is here. I'll greet them.

201
00:12:34,320 --> 00:12:36,130
Why does your face look red?

202
00:12:36,130 --> 00:12:37,240
I...

203
00:12:37,240 --> 00:12:39,220
I applied some makeup

204
00:12:39,220 --> 00:12:41,990
to showcase the school's image.

205
00:12:41,990 --> 00:12:43,210
Don't do it again.

206
00:12:43,210 --> 00:12:44,630
Okay!

207
00:12:49,970 --> 00:12:52,150
Hi, Mr. Zhang.

208
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,373
Shao Xue.

209
00:13:31,373 --> 00:13:33,240
The delegation is here. Let's go.

210
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:35,500
Okay. Let's go.

211
00:13:35,500 --> 00:13:37,390
Why does your face look redder than just now?

212
00:13:37,390 --> 00:13:39,750
It's so itchy. I scratched it.

213
00:13:39,750 --> 00:13:43,220
That's not right. It must be an allergic reaction.

214
00:13:43,220 --> 00:13:44,910
I'm fine. Let's go, sir.

215
00:13:44,910 --> 00:13:47,000
No. Go to the hospital.

216
00:13:47,000 --> 00:13:48,480
I'll take care of the delegation.

217
00:13:48,480 --> 00:13:49,620
Well...

218
00:13:49,620 --> 00:13:51,021
Stop babbling. Hurry up.

219
00:13:51,021 --> 00:13:52,450
I can do it, sir.

220
00:13:52,450 --> 00:13:54,750
Just go. I can take care of this. You take care of yourself!

221
00:13:54,750 --> 00:13:56,150
<i>[Dermatology]</i>

222
00:13:57,010 --> 00:13:59,350
This side. See?

223
00:14:00,150 --> 00:14:02,030
It's an allergy to some chemicals.

224
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:03,910
It's fine.

225
00:14:03,910 --> 00:14:06,670
But I can't guarantee full recovery.

226
00:14:07,690 --> 00:14:10,600
Then... will I be disfigured?

227
00:14:10,600 --> 00:14:13,240
Disfigured? It's too late to realize it. Scared now?

228
00:14:13,240 --> 00:14:16,170
How many times have I told you not to misuse cosmetics?

229
00:14:16,170 --> 00:14:17,950
Did you listen?

230
00:14:18,440 --> 00:14:19,873
Stop crying.

231
00:14:19,873 --> 00:14:20,970
You must not cry.

232
00:14:20,970 --> 00:14:22,840
Tears can irritate the skin.

233
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:24,620
Stop crying. Come on.

234
00:14:24,620 --> 00:14:27,840
Hold it back. Come on.

235
00:14:29,440 --> 00:14:33,030
Doctor, is there any way

236
00:14:33,030 --> 00:14:36,180
for my daughter to recover quickly?

237
00:14:36,940 --> 00:14:38,240
I'll prescribe her some medications.

238
00:14:38,240 --> 00:14:40,120
But she needs to work on it by herself.

239
00:14:40,120 --> 00:14:43,010
Don't eat stimulating food.

240
00:14:43,010 --> 00:14:44,320
Go to bed at a regular hour.

241
00:14:44,320 --> 00:14:45,670
Reduce mood swings.

242
00:14:45,670 --> 00:14:47,820
And apply the ointment on time.

243
00:14:47,820 --> 00:14:50,800
Generally, it shouldn't be a problem.

244
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:53,360
Did you hear it? Careful with what you eat.

245
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:55,310
Don't eat anything you shouldn't.

246
00:14:56,170 --> 00:15:01,210
By the way, don't touch the allergic area with your hands.

247
00:15:01,210 --> 00:15:02,683
Okay.

248
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:06,510
Feeling smug?

249
00:15:06,510 --> 00:15:07,600
Wearing makeup?

250
00:15:07,600 --> 00:15:08,960
I'll throw them away.

251
00:15:08,960 --> 00:15:11,620
Those are not cosmetics.

252
00:15:11,620 --> 00:15:14,590
Do it after the meal.

253
00:15:15,680 --> 00:15:16,720
She threw away my stuff.

254
